# VelocityPay Analytics Platform
## End-to-End Data Analytics & Machine Learning Case Study

---

# Project Summary

VelocityPay Analytics Platform is a complete end-to-end Data Analytics project developed for a fictional FinTech company.

The project simulates a real business environment where multiple business functions—including digital payments, subscriptions, SME lending, and product usage—generate operational data that must be transformed into actionable business insights.

The project demonstrates the complete analytics lifecycle, including data preparation, exploratory analysis, customer segmentation, machine learning, and interactive Power BI dashboards.

---

